code: import axios from'axios';const TravelPlan_API_BASE_URL="http://54.82.26.152:8088/api/v1/travelplans";class AdminService{getAllPlans(){return axios.get(TravelPlan_API_BASE_URL);}createPlan(travelPlan){return axios.post(TravelPlan_API_BASE_URL,travelPlan);}getPlanById(travelPlanId){return axios.get(TravelPlan_API_BASE_URL+'/'+travelPlanId);}updatePlan(travelPlan,travelPlanId){return axios.put(TravelPlan_API_BASE_URL+'/'+travelPlanId,travelPlan);}deletePlan(travelPlanId){return axios.delete(TravelPlan_API_BASE_URL+'/'+travelPlanId);}getRegisteredUsers(travelPlanId){return axios.get(TravelPlan_API_BASE_URL+'/'+travelPlanId+'/users');}}export default new AdminService();
